2003_July 14 

HOT SHOTS! (1991) *** Charlie Sheen, Cary Elwes, Valeria
Golino, Lloyd Bridges, Kevin Dunn, Jon Cryer, Kristy Swanson,
Efrem Zimablist, Jr. The &quot;Airplane!&quot; treatment of &quot;Top Gun&quot; with
Sheen perfectly dead-pan as a maverick fighter pilot and his
motley crew of oddballs.  Sightgags aplenty and Bridges is a riot
as the leader's surgically enhanced doofus.<br /><br />
